ttps://na.cx/i/QpugzkE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQpugzkE.jpg&h=ce685149&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Og2Fgy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOg2Fgy0.jpg&h=1d0a6914&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GtBuUkG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGtBuUkG.jpg&h=faf9b1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TqOUk0H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTqOUk0H.jpg&h=ba2beab5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQJX3d6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQJX3d6.jpg&h=4c305f1e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UxGe5st.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUxGe5st.jpg&h=1c77f3c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xLH2uT9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxLH2uT9.jpg&h=488a14d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bY3Ew7v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbY3Ew7v.jpg&h=46403871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"542f6569e6f779ae446983e01561bcdfca4d18f9","tid":2086771,"uid":53610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:23:45.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【手足歸位】一人一post宣傳七一遊行！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2079267\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2079267</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【每日任務】開post宣傳七一遊行 手足要歸位啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2080287\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2080287</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【七一遊行】一日一文宣 抗爭靠宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2081518\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2081518</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【倒數三日】七一遊行 一日一post宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2083270\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2083270</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【七一街頭見】我要文宣洗版呀屌你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2084470\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2084470</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a9f19411e0cf9ea1004afa3063cd325663d62260","tid":2086771,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:27:52.000Z","msg":"手足，大家聽日見，準備好道具比國際傳媒影啊<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=f5e8828f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱普城共諜放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"3bfdd91ee50fff3ad98d57cf98cc2166bfe85fbd","tid":2086771,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bb6075d780464dd836f9d56bd5ede2df92bb5cd","tid":2086771,"uid":181549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:32:39.000Z","msg":"最憎人遊行遲到<br />\n屌你次次睇到啲人被濫捕先話好嬲好嬲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4mx2u0m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4mx2u0m.jpg&h=89e4fbe4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8755d17a9c877ebab1b95975705621eadf0bf10d","tid":2086771,"uid":208122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:33:35.000Z","msg":"不見不散"},{"pid":"0d16601e965aa9fc9cffc10b4ed8d41303b7fbfa","tid":2086771,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T12:34:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad90112908a9844fc0325faa25c1c4d5f203e548","tid":2086771,"uid":288154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"【置頂】<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>選戰告急</strong></span></span> 倒數十星期 立即十星期拉票行動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2082608\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2082608</a><br />\n大家覺唔覺已被共匪立法引哂去，無人理9月6呢！"},{"pid":"0bacd308b0e645a83d77e29b5bdbc2b92b2c20e9","tid":2086771,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:29:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc0287b45457432a8f3fe6783b28efdcd07b1d60","tid":2086771,"uid":23993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T13:30:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkg